description: This Chainlink VRF common Anurak purrs with a rating of 32, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 96, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 3 for East, 1 for South, and 3 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20323-73133-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [96 Votes, Common]
